        <p class="mt-4 max-w-sm text-sm text-muted text-pretty">
          Verified software Bases — built and sold by Sarthak.
          Preview them, use them, buy the source, remix them with AI, or get help launching them.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 kicker-muted">Built, not curated. Honest, not infinite.</p>
